{"tid":2216156,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"教局打壓之手伸延 清算補習教師","createTime":"2020-09-24T13:01:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T16:14:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"01b97f8cd5c884b709209b8b22f123cd67923c3a","tid":2216156,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T13:01:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/SSX35NOMWBCGLCTJJXMCCKLYCA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2FSSX35NOMWBCGLCTJJXMCCKLYCA%2F&d=6i5jd82mnfhmr%2B7rEyOheDeipyOQHODmSSmjwmLFmyk%3D&h=22bbcfd1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2FSSX35NOMWBCGLCTJJXMCCKLYCA%2F&h=9eb80064\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/SSX35NOMWBCGLCTJJXMCCKLYCA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n教局打壓之手伸延 清算補習教師<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/verlXWZYxs89hgzT_6NHzh76w9o=/6720x4480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4Z5BXODGUNGNBJZ5FKP2ZY67R4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FverlXWZYxs89hgzT_6NHzh76w9o%3D%2F6720x4480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4Z5BXODGUNGNBJZ5FKP2ZY67R4.jpg&h=09020e8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■事發時任職現代教育的文靜因發表隱含「黑警死全家」字句帖文，遭教育局指專業失當。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】白色恐怖瀰漫教育界，教師於私人時間發表政治言論隨時被以言入罪，補習教師也未能倖免。有補習教師發表隱含「黑警死全家」字句的帖文後，遭教育局指專業失當。教育局重申，教師可有個人政治傾向，但發表意見時不應帶有仇恨。<br />\n<br />\n中文科補習教師文靜今年2月在私人社交賬戶發表帖文，內容指不解港人為何心腸狠毒、咒罵警察，並請年輕人發言前三思，然而串連每句的最尾一字，則成與文章意思相反的「黑警死全家 三萬thx！」。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n私人帖文被指咒警裁失當<br />\n<br />\n文靜發表後數小時即刪除，惟仍有人因此向教育局投訴。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n該信指文靜可於限期內提交書面解釋，她9月初解釋帖文有正面意思，且屬私人賬戶，惟暫未獲回覆。<br />\n<br />\n文靜的個人資料事後更被人放上「暴徒平台」，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n教育局拒評論個別個案。教局早前回應議員質詢表示，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n補習業界人士指，反修例運動期間，鮮有聽聞補習老師因政治言論被投訴或遭教育局調查。惟本月藝人鄧梓峰創辦的「梓峰教育」被指有老師在網課教授「武漢肺炎」，遭家長投訴後被炒，該補習社聲稱解僱因過往工作及考勤表現。"},{"pid":"6ca67dd7363b6d8c6acc7f5feacd96636916bca2","tid":2216156,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T16:14:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}